{"pin":"BH01352","subcodes":[{"code":"BH01352","anchor":"","first_line":"God willing, through the bounty of the True One, exalted be His glory, thou shalt quaff from the choice wine of divine knowledge and fix thy gaze upon the Most Exalted Horizon [3.5s]... ...Verily I say, this is the Day in which mankind can behold the Face, and hear the Voice, of the Promised One.... God grant that the light of unity may envelop the whole earth","first_line_orig":"انشاء الله بعنایت حق جل جلاله از رحیق عرفان بیاشامی و بافق اعلی ناظر باشی  ","language":"mixed","word_count":"630","subjects":"@suffering and imprisonment, @steadfastness; perseverance; faithfulness, @greatness and influence of the Cause; of this Day, @station of the Manifestation of God, @rejection by the people of the Bayan, @presence of; reunion with God, @call to unity; prohibition of disunity, @power and sovereignty of God; omnipotence of God","full_text_parts":["God grant that the light of unity may envelop the whole earth, and that the seal, “the Kingdom is God’s,” may be stamped upon the brow of all its peoples.\n\n\n* Gleanings, VII"],"translations":[]},{"code":"BH01352ADD","anchor":"add","translations":[{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"}]},{"code":"BH01352UNI","anchor":"uni","translations":[{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"kj","lang_name":"Oshikwanyama"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"naq","lang_name":"Khoekhoegowab"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"H